data.description: **Huge price reduction!! ** Welcome to Trailer Estates one of the most sought after active 55+ communities in the Bradenton area. The rarely available extra large corner lot with 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a fully enclosed Florida room has been tastefully updated throughout. This amazing home is being sold turnkey furnished (with the exception of main bedroom set and desk in the third bedroom). Upon entering the home you'll be so pleased to have a mudroom space with your washer and dryer indoors. No going outside to do laundry here! You will then fall in love with the high ceilings over the open concept kitchen, dining and living room combination. The perfect area's for entertaining. The home has the ideal split bedroom floorplan with large main bedroom with en-suite on one side of the home and the second and third bedroom on the other side of the home with their own bathroom. For some extra added peace of mind the home was WDO treated within the last year and the AC was replaced in 2020. Plenty of outside storage as well.                                                                                                                                                          Let's not forget about all the amazing amenities the community offers like an on site Marina (extra fee), swimming pool, pickleball, shuffle board, kayaking, dancing and community events that you'll never run out of things to do. All of this and you're only 10 minutes from the Sarasota airport, short ride to the areas best beaches and close to local restaurants and stores.                                                                                                       Hurry and schedule your appointment today to see this amazing home and community.
